{"type":"message","id":"5bfbc361","parentId":"2c5184ea","timestamp":"2026-04-04T08:59:56.505Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"日志看起来也正常，没有明显错误。让我直接问用户具体的情况，因为可能需要更多信息来诊断问题。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n日志看起来没明显错误。你说的\"卡死\"具体是哪种情况？\n\n- **发送消息后转圈加载** — 说明请求可能卡在模型调用那里\n- **收到回复后界面卡住** — 可能是渲染问题\n- **每次都卡还是偶尔？** \n\n能告诉我是怎么卡的吗？比如：\n1. 你发完消息，过多久开始卡的？\n2. 刷新页面能恢复吗？\n3. 换个渠道（比如从网页换到飞书）还卡吗？\n\n这样我能更准确定位问题 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":17894,"output":140,"cacheRead":1280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19314,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775293185398,"responseId":"019d57b83b3de8ab40bf7ea0f5205c82"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d3f30987","parentId":"5bfbc361","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:00:21.515Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-04-04 17:00 GMT+8] 为什么我用飞书给你发信息，发几次你就不回我了，检查一下"}],"timestamp":1775293221513}}
{"type":"message","id":"57a2a27b","parentId":"d3f30987","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:00:27.551Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说用飞书发信息，发几次我就不回他了。让我检查一下飞书频道的状态和会话情况。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d57b8d44a7a995df951ee228f359b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/openclaw status --deep 2>&1 | head -100","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":3322,"output":83,"cacheRead":15872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19277,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775293221515,"responseId":"019d57b8c83d36cf8e62dcf93b0a7b41"}}
