{"type":"message","id":"13ef57f2","parentId":"979e3902","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:04:48.690Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！现在我看到了：\n- 08:32:51 - 最后一条旧消息\n- 09:04:09 - **新消息到了！** 收到了\"测试\"消息并回复了\n- 09:04:11 - dispatch complete\n\n所以飞书连接是正常的，消息能收到也能回复。那问题可能是：\n1. 用户之前发消息时飞书 WebSocket 刚好断开了\n2. 或者飞书回调配置有时不稳定\n\n让我看看中间有没有 WebSocket 断开重连的记录。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好消息！刚刚收到你\"测试\"消息了，我也有回复！\n\n从日志看：\n- ✅ 09:04:09 收到消息\n- ✅ 09:04:11 发送回复\n\n所以飞书连接是正常的。**时好时坏的原因很可能是 WebSocket 连接不稳定**。\n\n让我查一下连接状态：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9b778df1e3e44749bee5ee7f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/openclaw logs --limit 2000 --timeout 15000 2>&1 | grep -iE \"(websocket|disconnect|reconnect|connection)\" | grep -v \"webchat\" | tail -25","timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":33911,"output":269,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34180,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775293483617,"responseId":"chatcmpl-96aa4ad0-3c4f-4062-be04-80587e73345f"}}
