{"type":"message","id":"dd789253","parentId":"b76d7a58","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:06:34.983Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看到了！`Restart=always`，这意味着 systemd 会在服务退出后自动重启。但这不会导致定期重启，只是会立即重启退出的服务。\n\n等一下，我看到日志里有 `gmail-watcher`。这可能是导致重启的原因 - 可能是 gmail-watcher 插件出了问题，导致整个 gateway 崩溃。\n\n让我看看日志中有没有更多关于 gmail-watcher 或者崩溃的信息。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d57bdb9f1b4f3b3f62bce3e7eaa26","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/openclaw logs --limit 5000 --max-bytes 400000 --timeout 20000 2>&1 | grep -iE \"(gmail|watchdog|crash|exit|oom)\" | tail -30","timeout":25}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":473,"output":169,"cacheRead":37504,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38146,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775293586451,"responseId":"019d57bda64180b7ec718bc557979e3c"}}
