{"type":"message","id":"b68aaa4b","parentId":"248339f3","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:07:13.695Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，找到了一个非常重要的线索！\n\n```\n{\"subsystem\":\"gateway/reload\"}\",\"1\":\"config change detected; evaluating reload (hooks.internal.entries.self-improvement.enabled)\n```\n\n这是 **config hot reload** 导致的重启！看起来是配置变化触发了重新加载。\n\n另外一个线索是：\n- `restart mode: full process restart (supervisor restart)` - 这是内部 supervisor 的重启\n\n让我查看一下是什么导致的 SIGTERM。从日志来看，SIGTERM 可能是：\n1. 外部系统发送的（systemd）\n2. 或者 OpenClaw 内部的 supervisor/restart 机制\n\n但是重启之前没有明显的错误。让我检查一下 systemd 日志，看是否能看到是什么触发 SIGTERM。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d57bf01d15ae30193158b2ae491d1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"journalctl --user -u openclaw-gateway --since \"2026-04-04 05:00\" --until \"2026-04-04 05:10\" 2>&1 | tail -30","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":6961,"output":217,"cacheRead":37888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45066,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775293610418,"responseId":"019d57beb71f909970223a62f786f907"}}
