{"type":"message","id":"8a5fc08e","parentId":"456dda9e","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:07:45.944Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到日志里有：- `config change detected; evaluating reload (hooks.internal.entries.self-improvement.enabled)`\n- `config hot reload applied (hooks.internal.entries.self-improvement.enabled)`\n\n这是配置热重载功能。当配置文件改变时，OpenClaw 会自动重载。但这不应该导致整个进程重启。\n\n让我检查一下是谁在修改配置文件导致的热重载。或者看看是否有某种 watchdog 或自动更新机制。\n\n实际上，我应该换个思路。让我直接问用户：你在 05:04 和 08:58 左右有没有手动操作过？比如运行 openclaw 命令？\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n找到关键线索了！\n\n从日志看到：\n```\nconfig change detected; evaluating reload (hooks.internal.entries.self-improvement.enabled)\nconfig hot reload applied\n```\n\n**原因很可能是**：系统有配置变更时自动热重载机制，但可能在某些情况下热重载不完整，导致进程需要完全重启。\n\n让我进一步排查：\n\n1. **你在 05:04 和 08:58 有没有运行过 openclaw 命令？**\n2. **或者有没有定时任务在修改配置？**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d57bf00163321e3313799f818d3f7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/.openclaw/*.json ~/.openclaw/config* 2>/dev/null | head -10","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":361,"output":267,"cacheRead":45952,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46580,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775293649264,"responseId":"019d57becae7512b6adad7967f2d28c1"}}
