{"type":"message","id":"592013ed","parentId":"03df59bb","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:07:55.202Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，最后检查版本的时间是 01:56，之后 gateway 在 05:04 被重启了。让我检查一下是否有自动更新机制。\n\n让我总结一下目前的发现：\n\n1. Gateway 每天定期重启多次（05:04, 08:58, 13:04, 16:58）\n2. 重启前有 config hot reload 的日志\n3. 重启是由 SIGTERM 信号触发的\n4. 没有找到 systemd 定时任务\n5. 可能是 OpenClaw 内部的 supervisor/restart 机制\n\n让我检查一下是否有更详细的日志来解释为什么重启。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dde6ce771885443abdb3fb9e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-04-04.log 2>/dev/null | grep -iE \"(supervisor|restart|reload)\" | head -20","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":46860,"output":193,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47053,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775293672052,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d1c223d0-a91d-4831-b8fc-6b922aa68520"}}
