{"type":"message","id":"f9f65282","parentId":"fc501b89","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:07:59.938Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了！根本原因已经明确了：**1. 配置变更触发重启**\n   - `config change requires gateway restart (plugins.entries.memory-lancedb) — deferring`\n   - 配置变化太大，需要完全重启 gateway\n   \n2. **重启流程**：\n   - `config change detected`\n   - 检测到需要重启\n   - `all operations and replies completed; restarting gateway now`   - `received SIGUSR1; restarting`\n   - `restart mode: full process restart (supervisor restart)`根本原因是：**配置文件被频繁修改**，导致 OpenClaw 检测到变化后需要重启 Gateway。\n\n让我看看是什么导致配置文件频繁变化。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n🎯 **找到根本原因了！**\n\n从日志看，问题很清楚：\n\n```\nconfig change requires gateway restart (plugins.entries.memory-lancedb)\n→ deferring until operations complete\n→ all operations completed; restarting gateway now\n→ received SIGUSR1; restarting  \n→ restart mode: full process restart (supervisor restart)\n```\n\n**原因是：配置文件被频繁修改，触发 Gateway 重启**\n\n让我查一下是什么在修改配置：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8f547404fefb458db0530d64","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la --time-style=full-iso ~/.openclaw/*.json 2>/dev/null","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":50788,"output":273,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51061,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775293675228,"responseId":"chatcmpl-02a55c23-a88f-48c0-a5b4-a5b33d910b61"}}
