{"type":"message","id":"577a8b71","parentId":"bc4d7747","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:08:04.702Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来 openclaw.json 可能是一些内部配置或 wizard 运行时生成的文件。让我查一下是什么导致配置文件变更。\n\n根据日志，触发重启的配置变更包括：\n- `plugins.entries.memory-lancedb` - 内存插件配置\n- `plugins.slots` - 插件槽位\n- `hooks.internal.entries.self-improvement.enabled` - hook 配置\n\n这看起来像是系统自动更新或某些插件的配置在变化。\n\n让我看看有没有什么进程在定期修改这些配置。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_af564a16f938455f9a23ed6f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"inotifywait -m ~/.openclaw 2>/dev/null -e modify -e create -e moved_to &\nsleep 5\necho \"--- monitoring ---\"\nkill %1 2>/dev/null","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":51549,"output":174,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51723,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775293681671,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b14dc5f3-3812-48b5-9620-15d94f0a7f33"}}
