{"type":"message","id":"f05bf461","parentId":"1205d9a0","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:08:16.451Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me summarize what we've found and explain to the user.\n\n总结发现：\n\n1. **根本原因**：OpenClaw 检测到配置文件变更后，会触发 Gateway 热重载。如果配置变更太大（如插件配置变化），会触发完全重启。\n\n2. **触发重启的配置变更**：\n   - `plugins.entries.memory-lancedb`\n   - `plugins.slots`\n   - `hooks.internal.entries.self-improvement.enabled`\n   - `plugins.entries.memory-lancedb.config.embedding.*`\n\n3. **重启流程**：\n   - 检测到配置变化\n   - 如果是大变化，defer 重启直到操作完成\n   - 重启后飞书 WebSocket 需要重新连接\n   - 这期间消息会丢失\n\n解决方案可能是：\n1. 找到是什么在修改配置（可能是某些插件或自动机制）\n2. 禁用某些会自动变化的配置\n3. 或者接受这种行为（配置热重载是特性不是 bug）\n\n但首先我需要找出是什么导致配置频繁变更。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 排查结果\n\n**根本原因找到了！**\n\n从日志分析，Gateway 定期重启的原因是：**配置文件被修改 → 触发热重载 → 重启**\n\n具体流程：\n```\nconfig change detected → config change requires gateway restart → \ndeferring until operations complete → all operations completed; \nrestarting gateway now → received SIGUSR1 → full process restart\n```\n\n**触发重启的配置项**：\n- `plugins.entries.memory-lancedb`\n- `plugins.slots`  \n- `hooks.internal.entries.self-improvement.enabled`\n\n---\n\n**问题**：是什么在修改这些配置？可能是：\n1. 某个插件在运行时自动更新配置\n2. 自动更新检查在修改配置\n3. 某种定时任务\n\n让我继续查：\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7e4e2572372d4694a08b7759","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find ~/.openclaw -name \"*.json\" -mtime -1 2>/dev/null | xargs ls -la 2>/dev/null","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":51751,"output":424,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52175,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775293689720,"responseId":"chatcmpl-211187d5-f511-4f97-98f4-0d4e1fdc6bef"}}
