{"type":"message","id":"bdb41640","parentId":"7f1e9a80","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:11:00.678Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the memory-lancedb plugin is disabled currently. When it was previously enabled (or attempted to be enabled), it was failing.\n\nNow I have a clear picture:\n\n1. **memory-lancedb** was being loaded but failing due to a path error - looking for `package.json` in `dist/` instead of the root `openclaw/` folder\n\n2. Each time it fails, the config is re-evaluated, triggering a gateway restart cycle\n\nLooking at the logs again:\n- 12:52:52 - memory-lancedb failed to load  \n- 12:55:15 - config change (plugins.entries.memory-lancedb)\n- 12:55:42 - config change again\n- 12:56:20 - config change again  \n- 12:56:43 - config change again  \n- 12:56:46 - gateway restart due to these changes\n- Then later at 13:03:40 - another config change (hooks.internal.entries.self-improvement.enabled) - perhaps self-improvement is also causing issues?\n\nThe root cause is a **plugin loading bug** in memory-lancedb. Since this keeps failing, it triggers repeated config changes → gateway restarts.\n\nLet me summarize the findings for the user.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 根本原因找到了！\n\n从日志分析，问题非常清晰：\n\n```\n12:52:52 memory-lancedb failed to load (Error: ENOENT: package.json in dist/)\n12:55:15 config change detected → plugins.entries.memory-lancedb\n12:55:42 config change detected → plugins.entries.memory-lancedb.config.embedding.xxx\n12:56:20 config change detected → plugins.slots\n12:56:43 config change detected → plugins.entries.memory-lancedb\n12:56:46 → Gateway 重启！\n```\n\n**问题根源**：\n\n1. **memory-lancedb 插件加载失败** — 找不到 `dist/package.json`\n2. **每次加载失败都触发配置变更** \n3. **配置变更累计到一定程度 → 触发 Gateway 重启**\n\n让我确认一下当前插件状态：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d57c1c9ce26f9ce1d575a807e0134","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/openclaw plugins list 2>&1 | grep -E \"(memory|Enabled|Disabled|Errors)\" | head -20","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":2272,"output":502,"cacheRead":54656,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57430,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775293835756,"responseId":"019d57c174eccf931c01084ce48adbe7"}}
