{"type":"message","id":"695b6d1d","parentId":"3c68b00a","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:11:09.453Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see - the memory-lancedb plugin is now disabled. The issue was happening earlier when it was trying to load.\n\nNow, let me see if there are other issues. Looking at the log, the second config change was:- hooks.internal.entries.self-improvement.enabled\n\nThis suggests that the self-improvement hook might also be modifying config. Let me check if there's something there.\n\nActually, the key finding is:1. memory-lancedb was failing to load\n2. Each failure triggers config change detection\n3. This causes restarts\n\nThe good news is that the plugin is now disabled. But we need to understand why it was being loaded in the first place and if there are other issues.\n\nLet me give the user a summary and recommend next steps.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n---\n\n## 📊 诊断总结\n\n| 问题 | 原因 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **memory-lancedb 加载失败** | 找不到 `dist/package.json` | ⚠️ 之前失败，已禁用 |\n| **配置频繁变更** | 插件加载失败触发配置重评 | ✅ 已停止 |\n| **Gateway 重启** | 配置变更累积触发热重载 | ✅ 暂时稳定 |\n\n**现在状态**：memory-lancedb 已禁用，Gateway 应该不会因为这个原因重启了。\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 验证\n\n刚才 09:04 测试成功了，说明飞书连接现在是稳定的。\n\n**不过**，还有一个潜在问题 — 从日志看还有一次配置变更：\n\n```\n13:03:40 config change: hooks.internal.entries.self-improvement.enabled\n```\n\n这说明 **self-improvement 钩子** 也在修改配置。让我检查一下：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c5707f3f8511434cb5a98578","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/self-improving/memory.md 2>/dev/null | head -30","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":57547,"output":386,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57933,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775293863603,"responseId":"chatcmpl-af101479-53f2-4e32-aef0-0bcda4d448f9"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c649968f","parentId":"695b6d1d","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:11:09.471Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c5707f3f8511434cb5a98578","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Self-Improving Memory\n\n## Confirmed Preferences\n<!-- Patterns confirmed by user, never decay -->\n\n## Active Patterns\n<!-- Patterns observed 3+ times, subject to decay -->\n\n## Recent (last 7 days)\n<!-- New corrections pending confirmation -->\n\n## 2026-04-04 - 长期记忆系统 (From 小八)\n\n### 核心概念\n- **MEMORY.md** = 长期记忆核心文件，每次会话自动加载\n- 文件即记忆：写进去的内容 = 永远记得\n- 三步流程：输入(你写) → 处理(AI读) → 维护(自动化)\n\n### 记忆层级\n| 层级 | 类比 | 存储位置 | 特点 |\n|------|------|----------|------|\n| 会话记忆 | 工作记忆 | 内存缓存 | 临时，会话结束即清空 |\n| 每日日志 | 短期日记 | memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md | 可跨会话，需主动调用 |\n| 长期记忆 | 核心知识库 | MEMORY.md | 每次会话自动加载，防失忆核心 |\n\n### 记忆插件\n- **memory-core**: 默认，开箱即用，够用\n- **LanceDB**: 专业版，更快更准的语义检索\n\n### 自动化 (可选)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":8,"aggregated":"# Self-Improving Memory\n\n## Confirmed Preferences\n<!-- Patterns confirmed by user, never decay -->\n\n## Active Patterns\n<!-- Patterns observed 3+ times, subject to decay -->\n\n## Recent (last 7 days)\n<!-- New corrections pending confirmation -->\n\n## 2026-04-04 - 长期记忆系统 (From 小八)\n\n### 核心概念\n- **MEMORY.md** = 长期记忆核心文件，每次会话自动加载\n- 文件即记忆：写进去的内容 = 永远记得\n- 三步流程：输入(你写) → 处理(AI读) → 维护(自动化)\n\n### 记忆层级\n| 层级 | 类比 | 存储位置 | 特点 |\n|------|------|----------|------|\n| 会话记忆 | 工作记忆 | 内存缓存 | 临时，会话结束即清空 |\n| 每日日志 | 短期日记 | memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md | 可跨会话，需主动调用 |\n| 长期记忆 | 核心知识库 | MEMORY.md | 每次会话自动加载，防失忆核心 |\n\n### 记忆插件\n- **memory-core**: 默认，开箱即用，够用\n- **LanceDB**: 专业版，更快更准的语义检索\n\n### 自动化 (可选)","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775293869468}}
{"type":"message","id":"7373f668","parentId":"c649968f","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:11:24.560Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the self-improvement system is working. That config change was legitimate - it's part of the hook functionality.Now let me summarize for the user. The main issue was the broken memory-lancedb plugin causing repeated restarts. The plugin is now disabled, so things should be stable.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 结论\n\n**主要问题已解决** — memory-lancedb 插件因为路径错误导致加载失败，每次失败都触发配置检测 → 累积触发重启。\n\n**现在是稳定的**：\n- memory-lancedb 已禁用\n- 飞书连接正常\n- Gateway 运行中\n\n---\n\n**后续建议**：\n1. 如果不需要 LanceDB 向量记忆功能，可以保持禁用 ✅\n2. 如果需要启用，需要修复插件路径问题（可能需要更新 OpenClaw 版本）\n\n需要我帮你做其他检查吗？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":2677,"output":170,"cacheRead":55552,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58399,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775293869472,"responseId":"019d57c2abab8ea915a3f44582299a30"}}
