{"type":"message","id":"fa437e7e","parentId":"58812bbd","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:15:28.915Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"小八在问 memory-core 是什么。这是一个简单的问题，直接回答即可。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**memory-core** 是 OpenClaw 内置的**默认记忆系统**。\n\n### 功能\n\n| 能力 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **文件存储** | 记忆保存在 `memory/*.md` 文件中 |\n| **全文搜索** | 关键词匹配搜索 |\n| **自动加载** | 每次会话自动读取 MEMORY.md |\n\n### 你的记忆文件结构\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/workspace/\n├── MEMORY.md              ← 核心长期记忆（每次会话自动加载）\n├── memory/\n│   ├── 2026-04-04.md      ← 今日日志\n│   └── 2026-04-03.md      ← 昨日日志\n├── self-improving/        ← 自我改进记忆（你的偏好、纠正）\n└── proactivity/           ← 主动性状态\n```\n\n### 工作方式\n\n1. **写入**：我把重要的事写进 `MEMORY.md` 或 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n2. **搜索**：你问我问题时，我会搜索相关记忆\n3. **加载**：新会话开始时自动读取 `MEMORY.md`\n\n---\n\n**你现在用的就是这个系统**，已经够用了 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":57599,"output":258,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57857,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775294123942,"responseId":"chatcmpl-7c6707bf-6874-4b3c-a6cd-1f8aa83fbfc1"}}
