{"type":"message","id":"45ad06c0","parentId":"3e9f240b","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:16:25.948Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if there's a way to have long-term and permanent memory capabilities. They're wondering why we need external plugins like memory-lancedb and whether memory-core can handle permanent/long-term memory.\n\nLet me explain the current setup more clearly:\n\n1. memory-core IS the long-term memory system - it stores memories in files that persist forever\n2. MEMORY.md is designed to be permanent memory\n3. The file-based approach IS long-term/permanent storage\n\nThe user might be confused about the terminology. Let me clarify:\n- memory-core provides long-term/permanent memory through files\n- The question is about the SEARCH capability, not the storage capability\n\nCurrently:\n- Files ARE permanent (they don't get deleted)\n- But search is keyword-based, not semantic\n\nIf they want semantic search (understanding meaning, not just keywords), then memory-lancedb is needed.\n\nLet me explain this clearly.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n有的！**memory-core 就是长期记忆系统**，记忆存在文件里是**永久的**。\n\n### 现有能力\n\n| 能力 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **永久存储** | ✅ | 写进 `MEMORY.md` 的内容永远在 |\n| **长期记忆** | ✅ | 文件不删除，会一直保留 |\n| **会话加载** | ✅ | 每次会话自动读取 MEMORY.md |\n\n### 区别在于搜索能力\n\n| 搜索方式 | memory-core | memory-lancedb |\n|----------|-------------|----------------|\n| **关键词** | ✅ | ✅ |\n| **语义理解** | ❌ | ✅ |\n\n### 举例说明\n\n假设记忆里有这句话：\n> \"小八住在望京京通大道\"\n\n**memory-core 搜索**：\n- 搜\"望京\" → 能找到 ✅\n- 搜\"家\" → 找不到 ❌（因为不含\"家\"字）\n- 搜\"住哪里\" → 找不到 ❌\n\n**memory-lancedb 搜索**：\n- 搜\"望京\" → 能找到 ✅\n- 搜\"家\" → 能找到 ✅（语义理解\"家\"≈\"住的地方\"）\n- 搜\"住哪里\" → 能找到 ✅\n\n---\n\n**总结**：\n- 你现在有**永久记忆能力** ✅（文件不会丢）\n- 但**语义搜索**能力有限（只能搜关键词）\n- 要更强的语义理解才需要 lancedb\n\n现在这样够用吗？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":5444,"output":505,"cacheRead":