{"type":"message","id":"3b188379","parentId":"f515243a","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:17:26.502Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if lancedb requires OpenAI API to work. Let me check the plugin config - it mentions OpenAI API Key but also supports custom baseUrl which could be compatible with other providers.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**不一定必须用 OpenAI**，lancedb 支持**多种 embedding provider**：\n\n### 支持的选项\n\n| Provider | API Key | 说明 |\n|----------|---------|------|\n| **OpenAI** | 需要 | 默认选项，模型 `text-embedding-3-small` |\n| **兼容 OpenAI 的 API** | 需要 | 比如 Cloudflare Workers AI、Ollama、本地部署等 |\n| **Azure OpenAI** | 需要 | 通过自定义 baseUrl |\n\n### 配置示例\n\n**用 OpenAI 官方**：\n```json\n{\n  \"embedding\": {\n    \"apiKey\": \"sk-xxx\",\n    \"model\": \"text-embedding-3-small\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**用本地 Ollama**（免费）：\n```json\n{\n  \"embedding\": {\n    \"apiKey\": \"不需要\",\n    \"baseUrl\": \"http://172.23.96.1:11434/v1\",\n    \"model\": \"mxbai-embed-large\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**用 Cloudflare Workers AI**（免费）：\n```json\n{\n  \"embedding\": {\n    \"apiKey\": \"你的 Cloudflare API Token\",\n    \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4\",\n    \"model\": \"@cf/baai/bge-base-en-v1.5\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n所以**不一定要用 OpenAI**，用本地 Ollama 或 Cloudflare 都可以免费用 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":23882,"output":341,"cacheRead":34432,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58655,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775294228567,"responseId":"019d57c78919187bcf7da5dc30a38a2d"}}
