{"type":"message","id":"f2d4de50","parentId":"fbe40e77","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:20:15.740Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see there's a `bge-m3:latest` model which is specifically an embedding model. Let me check the embedding API on Ollama.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n本地有 **bge-m3:latest** — 这是专业的 embedding 模型！\n\n### 本地 embedding 方案\n\n| 模型 | 用途 | 效果 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **bge-m3:latest** | 专用_embedding模型 | ⭐ 推荐 |\n| qwen2.5:14b | 聊天模型 | ❌ 不支持 embedding |\n\n**qwen2.5:14b 是对话模型，不支持 embedding**。\n\n### 推荐配置\n\n用 **bge-m3**（免费、效果好）：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"embedding\": {\n    \"apiKey\": \"不需要\",\n    \"baseUrl\": \"http://172.23.96.1:11434/v1\",\n    \"model\": \"bge-m3:latest\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### bge-m3 效果\n\n- 中英文语义理解都很强\n- 向量维度 1024\n- 比 OpenAI embedding 差一些，但**免费**且**本地速度快**\n\n---\n\n要我帮你配置 lancedb 用本地 bge-m3 吗？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1153,"output":253,"cacheRead":58624,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60030,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775294399193,"responseId":"019d57cac1086daffe5812d4ddb5f9ef"}}
