{"type":"message","id":"eef84666","parentId":"5adf81fd","timestamp":"2026-04-04T09:23:04.114Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to help configure lancedb with the local bge-m3 model. Let me do that.\n\nI need to:\n1. First check the current lancedb config\n2. Update it with the bge-m3 settings\n\nBut I also need to remember the issue we found earlier - memory-lancedb was failing to load because it couldn't find dist/package.json. Let me first check if that's still an issue, and if so, we may need to fix that first.\n\nLet me check the current plugin status and try to enable/configure lancedb.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_781c6b27fae04c65bbb77e7e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/openclaw config get plugins.entries.memory-lancedb 2>&1","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":60003,"output":179,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60182,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775294580925,"responseId":"chatcmpl-87b79519-efc7-4130-b04c-2f69dea78aa5"}}
