{"type":"message","id":"49eb2dff","parentId":"66659dd6","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:22:39.048Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d5916b1ac0da403e18d7421df1a30","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"for (const legacy of LEGACY_STATE_DIRS) {\n\t\tconst candidate = join(home, legacy, \"memory\", \"lancedb\");\n\t\ttry {\n\t\t\tif (fsSync.existsSync(candidate)) return candidate;\n\t\t} catch {}\n\t}\n\treturn preferred;\n}\nconst DEFAULT_DB_PATH = resolveDefaultDbPath();\nconst EMBEDDING_DIMENSIONS = {\n\t\"text-embedding-3-small\": 1536,\n\t\"text-embedding-3-large\": 3072\n};\nfunction assertAllowedKeys(value, allowed, label) {\n\tconst unknown = Object.keys(value).filter((key) => !allowed.includes(key));\n\tif (unknown.length === 0) return;\n\tthrow new Error(`${label} has unknown keys: ${unknown.join(\", \")}`);\n}\nfunction vectorDimsForModel(model) {\n\tconst dims = EMBEDDING_DIMENSIONS[model];\n\tif (!dims) throw new Error(`Unsupported embedding model: ${model}`);"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9,"aggregated":"for (const legacy of LEGACY_STATE_DIRS) {\n\t\tconst candidate = join(home, legacy, \"memory\", \"lancedb\");\n\t\ttry {\n\t\t\tif (fsSync.existsSync(candidate)) return candidate;\n\t\t} catch {}\n\t}\n\treturn preferred;\n}\nconst DEFAULT_DB_PATH = resolveDefaultDbPath();\nconst EMBEDDING_DIMENSIONS = {\n\t\"text-embedding-3-small\": 1536,\n\t\"text-embedding-3-large\": 3072\n};\nfunction assertAllowedKeys(value, allowed, label) {\n\tconst unknown = Object.keys(value).filter((key) => !allowed.includes(key));\n\tif (unknown.length === 0) return;\n\tthrow new Error(`${label} has unknown keys: ${unknown.join(\", \")}`);\n}\nfunction vectorDimsForModel(model) {\n\tconst dims = EMBEDDING_DIMENSIONS[model];\n\tif (!dims) throw new Error(`Unsupported embedding model: ${model}`);","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775316159041}}
{"type":"message","id":"37427201","parentId":"49eb2dff","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:22:43.567Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see. The plugin only supports these models:\n- text-embedding-3-small: 1536 dimensions\n- text-embedding-3-large: 3072 dimensions\n\nIt doesn't support bge-m3. The plugin is hardcoded to only support OpenAI's embedding models.\n\nWe have two options:1. Switch to using text-embedding-3-small with OpenAI API (costs money)2. Use a different approach - maybe we can configure a custom model that works with the Ollama embeddings\n\nActually, wait - let me check if there's any way to use custom embedding models. The plugin seems to only support the OpenAI format.\n\nLet me first switch back to memory-core since lancedb doesn't support local models. This is a limitation of the current plugin.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ce8a4df110a041af80fabb91","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -r \"text-embedding\" ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/config-CldCnqOx.js 2>/dev/null | head -10","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":68458,"output":235,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68693,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775316159049,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ed1a7c1b-fa55-4d7c-897f-01736781e377"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6b194422","parentId":"37427201","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:22:43.601Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ce8a4df110a041af80fabb91","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"const DEFAULT_MODEL = \"text-embedding-3-small\";\n\t\"text-embedding-3-small\": 1536,\n\t\"text-embedding-3-large\": 3072"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":12,"aggregated":"const DEFAULT_MODEL = \"text-embedding-3-small\";\n\t\"text-embedding-3-small\": 1536,\n\t\"text-embedding-3-large\": 3072","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775316163595}}
{"type":"message","id":"3a17e19a","parentId":"6b194422","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:23:00.577Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"确认了：lancedb 插件只支持 OpenAI 的 embedding 模型：- text-embedding-3-small (1536维)\n- text-embedding-3-large (3072维)\n\n本地 bge-m3 不支持。让我告诉用户并帮他切换回 memory-core：\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**不支持！** \n\nlancedb 插件只认这两个模型：\n\n| 模型 | 维度 |\n|------|------|\n| text-embedding-3-small | 1536 |\n| text-embedding-3-large | 3072 |\n\n**bge-m3 用不了**，插件不支持本地模型。\n\n---\n\n### 方案\n\n1. **用 OpenAI** — 配置 apiKey，用官方模型（收费）\n2. **放弃 lancedb** — 用回 memory-core（免费，继续用关键词搜索）\n\n要切换回 memory-core 吗？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":622,"output":175,"cacheRead":68096,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68893,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775316163603,"responseId":"019d5916d91f6bd3ae84c1e28ffadbef"}}
{"type":"message","id":"588ac0d8","parentId":"3a17e19a","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:25:50.707Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-04-04 23:25 GMT+8] 这个怎么样：直接「拥抱原生」，使用LanceDB的本地模型支持\n这是最直接、也最彻底的解决方案：抛弃那个受限的插件，直接使用 LanceDB 的 Python SDK。\n\nLanceDB 对 Hugging Face 生态和 Sentence Transformers 提供了原生支持，让你可以直接调用海量的本地模型。\n\n操作示例：\n\npython\nimport lancedb\nfrom lancedb.pydantic import LanceModel, Vector\nfrom lancedb.embeddings import get_registry\n\n# 1. 从LanceDB的注册中心获取本地模型\nmodel = get_registry().get(\"sentence-transformers\").create(\n name=\"BAAI/bge-small-zh-v1.5\", # 一个优秀的中文模型\n device=\"cpu\" # 或 \"cuda\" 使用GPU\n)\n\n# 2. 定义数据库表结构\nclass Documents(LanceModel):\n text: str = model.SourceField() # 原文，会被自动嵌入\n vector: Vector(model.ndims()) = model.VectorField() # 存储的向量\n\n# 3. 连接数据库并创建表\ndb = lancedb.connect(\"/tmp/lancedb\")\ntable = db.create_table(\"my_docs\", schema=Documents, mode=\"overwrite\")\n\n# 4. 添加数据（嵌入会自动在后台生成）\ntable.add([{\"text\": \"你的第一个文档。\"}, {\"text\": \"这是第二个示例。\"}])\n\n# 5. 查询（查询文本的嵌入也会自动生成）\nresults = table.search(\"查询示例\").limit(3).to_list()"}],"timestamp":1775316350699}}
{"type":"message","id":"be9ffba9","parentId":"588ac0d8","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:25:53.981Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想用原生 Python + LanceDB 来实现本地 embedding，绕过 OpenClaw 插件的限制。这是个好主意！可以用 Python 脚本直接调用 LanceDB + sentence-transformers 模型。\n\n但这需要：\n1. 安装 Python 的 lancedb 和 sentence-transformers\n2. 创建一个独立的 Python 脚本来管理记忆\n3. 可能需要在 OpenClaw 之外手动同步记忆\n\n让我帮用户实现这个方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好主意！用原生 Python + LanceDB 可以绕过插件限制，用本地模型。\n\n让我帮你搭：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ecbea25c3b4745cbb46f6cb1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"pip3 show lancedb 2>/dev/null | head -3 || pip3 install lancedb sentence-transformers -q 2>&1 | tail -5","timeout":120}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":68977,"output":177,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69154,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775316350703,"responseId":"chatcmpl-fd87181c-ad06-4bcc-8b3f-f40a9eac0123"}}
