{"type":"message","id":"e70d72e0","parentId":"dd9f7cc2","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:31:19.443Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It's still running. Let me just provide the Python script for the user to run manually. The installation might be slow due to downloading many packages.\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n安装比较慢，我先给你写好脚本，你手动运行：\n\n```python\n# ~/memory-lancedb.py\nimport lancedb\nfrom lancedb.pydantic import LanceModel, Vector\nfrom lancedb.embeddings import get_registry\n\n# 模型 - bge-small-zh-v1.5 是中文小模型，速度快\nmodel = get_registry().get(\"sentence-transformers\").create(\n    name=\"BAAI/bge-small-zh-v1.5\",\n    device=\"cpu\"\n)\n\nclass Doc(LanceModel):\n    text: str = model.SourceField()\n    vector: Vector(model.ndims()) = model.VectorField()\n    source: str  # 记忆来源\n\nDB_PATH = \"/home/ai/.openclaw/memory/lancedb\"\n\ndef init_db():\n    db = lancedb.connect(DB_PATH)\n    # 如果表已存在就跳过\n    try:\n        db.create_table(\"memory\", schema=Doc, mode=\"overwrite\")\n        print(\"✅ 数据库创建成功\")\n    except:\n        print(\"📂 数据库已存在\")\n    return db\n\ndef add_memory(text, source=\"manual\"):\n    db = lancedb.connect(DB_PATH)\n    table = db.open_table(\"memory\")\n    table.add([Doc(text=text, source=source)])\n    print(f\"✅ 添加记忆: {text[:30]}...\")\n\ndef search_memory(query, top_k=3):\n    db = lancedb.connect(DB_PATH)\n    table = db.open_table(\"memory\")\n    results = table.search(query, vector_column_name=\"vector\").limit(top_k).to_list()\n    return results\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    init_db()\n    # 测试\n    add_memory(\"小八住在望京，是北京的一个地方\", source=\"test\")\n    results = search_memory(\"小八住在哪里\")\n    for r in results:\n        print(f\"- {r['text']} (距离: {r['distance']:.4f})\")\n```\n\n---\n\n安装完成后运行：\n```bash\npip3 install lancedb sentence-transformers\npython3 ~/memory-lancedb.py\n```\n\n安装好告诉我，我帮你测试 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":319,"output":477,"cacheRead":69376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70172,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775316653163,"responseId":"019d591dcfa160239e7f4ed8fb39e068"}}
