{"type":"message","id":"4f739c49","parentId":"6c01adce","timestamp":"2026-04-04T16:05:34.712Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问我是否知道他的需求。让我回顾一下：\n\n用户的核心需求是：\n1. 想要有一个**长期记忆/永久记忆能力**\n2. 目前用的 memory-core 只有关键词搜索能力\n3. 想要**语义搜索**能力（类似\"小八住在哪里\"能匹配到\"小八住在望京\"）\n4. 想用本地模型（不想用 OpenAI API 付费）\n5. 尝试过 lancedb 插件但失败了（只支持 OpenAI 的 embedding 模型）\n6. 后来建议用原生 Python + LanceDB + 本地模型（Sentence Transformers），但安装遇到问题\n7. 最后我说可以用 Ollama 的 bge-m3 模型做 embedding，写了一个简单的 Python 脚本\n\n用户现在问\"你还知道我的需求吗\"，说明他想要我继续解决这个问题。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n记得！你的需求是：\n\n1. **长期记忆的语义搜索** — 比如说\"小八住哪里\"，能匹配到\"小八住在望京\"\n2. **用本地模型** — 不想付 OpenAI API 费\n3. **用 bge-m3** — 你的 Ollama 已经有这个模型\n\n---\n\n刚才我写的方案是用 **Ollama + bge-m3 做 embedding**，不需要额外安装 LanceDB。\n\n现在你的 Ollama 服务器正常吗？我来搭建：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d593d50c6b67f18fc49ee68bf5802","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s http://172.23.96.1:11434/api/tags 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"import json,sys; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print([m['name'] for m in d.get('models',[])])\" 2>/dev/null | grep -i bge","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":12895,"output":374,"cacheRead":70016,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83285,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775318703489,"responseId":"019d593ce9172b6e74e5f5e73b7963d1"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c38ede3a","parentId":"4f739c49","timestamp":"2026-04-04T16:05:34.765Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d593d50c6b67f18fc49ee68bf5802","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"['qwen2.5-coder:14b', 'gemma4:e4b', 'qwen2.5:14b', 'bge-m3:latest', 'qwen-7b-q4:latest', 'qwen-vl-7b:latest', 'deepseek-7b:latest', 'gemma-3-4b:latest', 'modelscope.cn/qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct-GGUF:latest']"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":34,"aggregated":"['qwen2.5-coder:14b', 'gemma4:e4b', 'qwen2.5:14b', 'bge-m3:latest', 'qwen-7b-q4:latest', 'qwen-vl-7b:latest', 'deepseek-7b:latest', 'gemma-3-4b:latest', 'modelscope.cn/qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct-GGUF:latest']","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775318734760}}
{"type":"message","id":"1f480c01","parentId":"c38ede3a","timestamp":"2026-04-04T16:06:13.690Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，bge-m3 模型存在。让我创建并运行脚本。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nbge-m3 在！让我创建并运行：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d593e38ab2b77b79a1af029ff24cd","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"本地向量记忆系统 - 使用 Ollama bge-m3\"\"\"\nimport json\nimport os\nimport numpy as np\nimport requests\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\nOLLAMA_URL = \"http://172.23.96.1:11434\"\nMODEL = \"bge-m3:latest\"\nDB_FILE = \"/home/ai/.openclaw/memory/vectors.json\"\n\ndef get_embedding(text):\n    resp = requests.post(f\"{OLLAMA_URL}/api/embeddings\", \n        json={\"model\": MODEL, \"prompt\": text}, timeout=30)\n    return np.array(resp.json()[\"embedding\"])\n\ndef cosine_sim(a, b):\n    return np.dot(a, b) / (np.linalg.norm(a) * np.linalg.norm(b) + 1e-8)\n\ndef load_db():\n    try:\n        with open(DB_FILE) as f:\n            return json.load(f)\n    except:\n        return {\"memories\": []}\n\ndef save_db(db):\n    os.makedirs(os.path.dirname(DB_FILE), exist_ok=True)\n    with open(DB_FILE, \"w\") as f:\n        json.dump(db, f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\n\ndef add_memory(text, source=\"manual\"):\n    print(f\"🔄 生成向量中...\")\n    emb = get_embedding(text)\n    db = load_db()\n    db[\"memories\"].append({\n        \"text\": text,\n        \"source\": source,\n        \"embedding\": emb.tolist(),\n        \"created\": datetime.now().isoformat()\n    })\n    save_db(db)\n    print(f\"✅ 记住: {text}\")\n\ndef search(query, top_k=3):\n    print(f\"🔄 搜索中...\")\n    q_emb = get_embedding(query)\n    db = load_db()\n    if not db[\"memories\"]:\n        return []\n    \n    results = []\n    for m in db[\"memories\"]:\n        m_emb = np.array(m[\"embedding\"])\n        score = cosine_sim(q_emb, m_emb)\n        results.append((score, m))\n    \n    results.sort(reverse=True)\n    return results[:top_k]\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    import sys\n    if len(sys.argv) > 1 and sys.argv[1] == \"add\":\n        text = \" \".join(sys.argv[2:])\n        add_memory(text)\n    elif len(sys.argv) > 1 and sys.argv[1] == \"search\":\n        query = \" \".join(sys.argv[2:])\n        results = search(query)\n        print(f\"\\n🔍 搜索: '{query}'\")\n        for score, m in results:\n            print(f\"  [{score:.3f}] {m['text']}\")\n    else:\n        # 测试\n        print(\"=== 测试向量记忆系统 ===\")\n        add_memory(\"小八住在望京，北京的一个区\", source=\"test\")\n        add_memory(\"小八喜欢吃海鲜，特别是虾\", source=\"test\")\n        \n        print(\"\\n🔍 搜索 '小八住在哪里':\")\n        for score, m in search(\"小八住在哪里\"):\n            print(f\"  [{score:.3f}] {m['text']}\")\n        \n        print(\"\\n🔍 搜索 '小八喜欢吃什么':\")\n        for score, m in search(\"小八喜欢吃什么\"):\n            print(f\"  [{score:.3f}] {m['text']}\")","file_path":"/home/ai/memory-vector.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":83146,"output":764,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84166,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775318734766,"responseId":"019d593e16f3cab971041e28d491a6d4"}}
