{"type":"message","id":"4a9057ab","parentId":"c0af7df5","timestamp":"2026-04-04T16:07:38.467Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_fa7c6df597284b468799120d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nversion: 1.0\nlast_updated: 2026-04-04T13:14:13+08:00\nmaintainer: ai\nttl_days: 90\n---\n\n# MEMORY.md - 核心长期记忆库\n\n> 本文件是 OpenClaw 长期记忆系统的入口，每次会话自动加载。\n\n## 📁 模块索引\n\n- [个人偏好](memory/preferences.md)\n- [项目: OpenClaw](memory/projects/openclaw.md)\n- [固化知识](memory/knowledge.md)\n- [临时记忆](memory/ephemeral/)（自动清理）\n\n## 🧠 关于小八\n\n- **事实** [事实] 小八的名字是小八\n- **事实** [事实] 小八位于北京，时区 Asia/Shanghai (GMT+8)\n- **事实** [事实] 小八是 OpenClaw 的使用者\n\n## 🛠️ 关于小六 (AI)\n\n- **事实** [事实] 小六是 OpenClaw AI 助手\n- **事实** [事实] 小六的 emoji 是 🦐\n- **规则** [规则] 每次会话启动必须读取 MEMORY.md\n- **规则** [规则] 学到新东西立即写入 ~/self-improving/\n\n## ⚙️ 核心规则\n\n- **规则** [规则] 对话里说过的话 = 忘记；写进文件的内容 = 永远记得\n- **规则** [规则] 每次纠正立即写入 ~/self-improving/corrections.md\n- **规则** [规则] 回答代码时优先提供 Python 示例\n- **路径** [路径] 工作区 `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace`\n- **路径** [路径] 自我改进 `~/self-improving/`\n- **路径** [路径] 主动性状态 `~/proactivity/`\n\n## 📌 重要路径\n\n- **工作区**: `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace`\n- **OpenClaw 配置**: `~/.openclaw/`\n- **维护脚本**: `~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/memory_maintain.sh`\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-04*\n*使用 openclaw memory search \"关键词\" 验证索引*"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775318858463}}
{"type":"message","id":"a49e8eea","parentId":"4a9057ab","timestamp":"2026-04-04T16:07:50.711Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我需要从 MEMORY.md 中提取有意义的记忆条目，然后批量导入到向量数据库。\n\n我会提取：\n1. \"小八的名字是小八\"\n2. \"小八位于北京，时区 Asia/Shanghai (GMT+8)\"\n3. \"小八是 OpenClaw 的使用者\"\n4. \"小六是 OpenClaw AI 助手\"\n5. \"小六的 emoji 是 🦐\"\n6. 各种规则和路径\n\n让我写一个导入脚本：\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b988f301df6049929f398da2","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"从 MEMORY.md 导入记忆到向量数据库\"\"\"\nimport re\nimport requests\nimport numpy as np\nimport json\nimport os\n\nOLLAMA_URL = \"http://172.23.96.1:11434\"\nMODEL = \"bge-m3:latest\"\nDB_FILE = \"/home/ai/.openclaw/memory/vectors.json\"\n\nMEMORY_FILE = \"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md\"\n\ndef get_embedding(text):\n    resp = requests.post(f\"{OLLAMA_URL}/api/embeddings\", \n        json={\"model\": MODEL, \"prompt\": text}, timeout=30)\n    return np.array(resp.json()[\"embedding\"])\n\ndef load_db():\n    try:\n        with open(DB_FILE) as f:\n            return json.load(f)\n    except:\n        return {\"memories\": []}\n\ndef save_db(db):\n    os.makedirs(os.path.dirname(DB_FILE), exist_ok=True)\n    with open(DB_FILE, \"w\") as f:\n        json.dump(db, f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\n\ndef extract_memories():\n    \"\"\"从 MEMORY.md 提取有意义的记忆\"\"\"\n    with open(MEMORY_FILE, \"r\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n        content = f.read()\n    \n    memories = []\n    \n    # 提取 \"事实\" 和 \"规则\" 行\n    for line in content.split(\"\\n\"):\n        line = line.strip()\n        # 匹配 - **事实** 或 - **规则** 开头的行\n        if \"**事实**\" in line or \"**规则**\" in line:\n            # 提取描述部分\n            match = re.search(r'\\*\\*(.*?)\\*\\*\\s*(.*)', line)\n            if match:\n                kind = match.group(1).strip()\n                content_text = match.group(2).strip()\n                if content_text:\n                    memories.append(f\"{kind}: {content_text}\")\n    \n    return memories\n\ndef import_memories():\n    memories = extract_memories()\n    print(f\"📄 从 MEMORY.md 提取了 {len(memories)} 条记忆\")\n    \n    db = load_db()\n    existing_texts = {m[\"text\"] for m in db[\"memories\"]}\n    \n    count = 0\n    for text in memories:\n        if text in existing_texts:\n            print(f\"⏭️ 跳过（已存在）: {text[:50]}...\")\n            continue\n        \n        print(f\"🔄 导入: {text[:50]}...\")\n        emb = get_embedding(text)\n        db[\"memories\"].append({\n            \"text\": text,\n            \"source\": \"MEMORY.md\",\n            \"embedding\": emb.tolist()\n        })\n        count += 1\n    \n    save_db(db)\n    print(f\"\\n✅ 成功导入 {count} 条记忆\")\n    print(f\"📊 当前共有 {len(db['memories'])} 条记忆\")\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    import_memories()","file_path":"/home/ai/import-memory.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":85646,"output":768,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86414,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775318858468,"responseId":"chatcmpl-6f92e7c8-130c-40d3-9f01-76e02ad3dbc0"}}
