{"type":"message","id":"bfa36bca","parentId":"c691c55f","timestamp":"2026-04-04T16:10:09.437Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在可以列出所有记忆了。让我告诉用户怎么使用自动记忆功能。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n✅ **自动记忆已就绪！**\n\n### 使用方法\n\n| 操作 | 命令 |\n|------|------|\n| 记住新东西 | `python3 ~/memory-vector.py add \"内容\"` |\n| 搜索记忆 | `python3 ~/memory-vector.py search \"关键词\"` |\n| 查看所有 | `python3 ~/memory-vector.py list` |\n\n### 示例\n\n```bash\n# 记住新知识\npython3 ~/memory-vector.py add \"小八在望京SOHO工作\"\n\n# 搜索\npython3 ~/memory-vector.py search \"小八在哪里工作\"\n```\n\n**现在你可以直接对我说 \"记住 xxx\"，我来帮你存！**\n\n比如：\n> \"记住小八今天加班到晚上10点\"\n\n要我帮你存什么吗？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":88382,"output":174,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88812,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775318993610,"responseId":"019d59416a3ca2c4ef81cf9135ba0a6c"}}
