{"type":"message","id":"cfb76369","parentId":"6d78c59e","timestamp":"2026-04-04T16:15:23.959Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I found it. There's a \"safeguard\" mode that's currently enabled. This is OpenClaw's built-in context compaction. Let me explain this to the user.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**有！** OpenClaw 内置了**上下文压缩**功能。\n\n### 当前状态\n\n你已经在用了：\n\n```\nagents.defaults.compaction.mode = \"safeguard\"\n```\n\n### 工作方式\n\n| 模式 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **safeguard** (当前) | 当上下文快满时，自动压缩旧内容成摘要 |\n| **default** | 不自动压缩 |\n\n### 触发条件\n\n当对话太长要超过 context limit 时，会自动：\n1. 把之前的对话压缩成**简短摘要**\n2. 保留关键信息（事实、决定、偏好）\n3. 释放空间继续对话\n\n---\n\n**你现在用的就是 safeguard 模式**，已经开启了智能压缩 ✅\n\n要调整设置吗？比如：\n- 改成更激进的压缩\n- 用更好的模型做摘要（目前默认）\n\n🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1328,"output":211,"cacheRead":92288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93827,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775319312425,"responseId":"019d59464ac3379907c457c4d925facf"}}
{"type":"message","id":"99f0263a","parentId":"cfb76369","timestamp":"2026-04-04T16:15:49.459Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-04-05 00:15 GMT+8] 解释一下"}],"timestamp":1775319349451}}
{"type":"message","id":"cb29ad36","parentId":"99f0263a","timestamp":"2026-04-04T16:16:03.874Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想让我更详细解释上下文压缩功能。让我更详细地解释一下。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n### 上下文压缩解释\n\n#### 问题\n对话越来越长，会消耗大量 token，最后：\n- 💰 **费钱** — 按 token 收费\n- 📊 **超限** — 超过模型的 context limit（你的 205k）\n\n#### 解决方案：safeguard 模式\n\n当 token 快用完时，OpenClaw 会：\n\n```\n原始对话（100条消息）\n        ↓\n[自动压缩] ← 用 AI 提取关键信息\n        ↓\n压缩后摘要（5条消息）\n        ↓\n继续对话\n```\n\n#### 压缩保留什么？\n\n| 保留 | 删除 |\n|------|------|\n| ✅ 重要事实 | ❌ 客套话 |\n| ✅ 你的偏好 | ❌ 重复确认 |\n| ✅ 决定/承诺 | ❌ 过程细节 |\n| ✅ 代码/配置 | ❌ 调试日志 |\n\n#### 你的配置\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"compaction\": {\n        \"mode\": \"safeguard\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**目前是安全的自动模式**，不用管它，会自动处理 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1616,"output":257,"cacheRead":92032,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93905,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775319349457,"responseId":"019d5946c55fbd36ca1705c409e1c172"}}
{"type":"message","id":"59165c0a","parentId":"cb29ad36","timestamp":"2026-04-04T16:17:00.080Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-04-05 00:16 GMT+8] 你可以让你变的更鲁棒吗"}],"timestamp":1775319420066}}
{"type":"message","id":"8877d070","parentId":"59165c0a","timestamp":"2026-04-04T16:17:04.049Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在问我能不能让自己变得更鲁棒（健壮）。这可能是指：\n1. 让我（AI助手）自己更稳定、更不容易出错\n2. 增加更多的错误处理和恢复机制\n3. 让我能自动修复问题\n\n我可以做一些事情来让对话更稳定，比如：\n1. 减少长时间运行的命令\n2. 增加错误处理\n3. 让一些操作更安全\n\n不过用户可能也想让我有更多的自我修复能力。我可以检查一下当前的会话状态，看看有没有什么问题。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n可以！让我增强一下稳定性：\n\n1. **减少长时间运行的命令** — 避免 pip install 卡死\n2. **增加超时保护** \n3. **自动错误恢复**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e98a8ac271434a9284780430","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/openclaw status 2>&1 | grep -iE \"(session|error|warning)\" | head -10","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":94037,"output":210,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94247,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775319420072,"responseId":"chatcmpl-27d57ec8-edf2-4acb-9046-8f75ea127346"}}
