{"type":"message","id":"66bbb139","parentId":"9aa8143c","timestamp":"2026-04-04T16:19:33.086Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"一切正常！让我给用户一个总结，说一下我可以怎么变得更鲁棒。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n✅ **现在我很鲁棒！**\n\n### 验证结果\n\n```\n✅ Ollama (embedding)  - 9个模型, bge-m3 有\n✅ 向量记忆            - 14条记忆\n✅ OpenClaw Gateway   - 运行中\n```\n\n### 让我更鲁棒的方法\n\n| 能力 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **本地向量记忆** | ✅ | 不依赖外部服务，断网也能搜 |\n| **上下文压缩** | ✅ | safeguard 模式自动处理长对话 |\n| **飞书连接** | ✅ | WebSocket 实时在线 |\n| **健康检查** | ✅ | 一键诊断问题 |\n\n### 快速检查命令\n\n```bash\n# 检查整体状态\npython3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/health-check.py\n\n# 搜记忆\npython3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/memory-tool.py search \"关键词\"\n\n# 查看所有记忆\npython3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/memory-tool.py list\n```\n\n---\n\n以后如果我有问题，你可以说\"检查一下\"，我就会跑这个健康检查 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":833,"output":246,"cacheRead":96256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97335,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775319558391,"responseId":"019d594aa7cd78d32cdff412aade23b0"}}
